  "text": "The data from this research comes from Spanish informants. An interesting avenue for future research would be to examine the potential impact that the different cultural and national contexts have on challenging OCB, articulating and examining the effects of cultural differences in the relationships between the change-oriented OCB and its antecedents. Finally, future research could consider expanded versions of the proposed conceptual model, that can include other constructs such as other subdimensions of transformational leadership [CITATION_1] , personality characteristics included in the Big Five Model, or proactive personality as a moderator of these relationships, ",
